description: CōTZ PEDIATRIC with Gentle Mineral Complex is Paediatrician Recommended to protect children’s thinner skin from damaging sun rays. Pediatrician Recommended: Suitable for Infants, Toddlers & School-Age children (age: 6+ months) A Gentle Mineral Complex that helps prevent heat build-up in children’s skin, which can damage the dermis.
